          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1659433177762-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>black bean paste</strong>, <strong>cornflour </strong>and <strong>remaining five-spice mix</strong> in a small bowl</p><p>Add your<strong> sriracha </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> and <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong> with 50ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[75ml] </span>[100ml] </span><strong>cold water </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]<strong> </span>sugar </strong>and mix it all together – this is your <strong>black bean sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1659433182290-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1659433182290-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1659433182290-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1659433182290-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1659433182290-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped pepper</strong>,<strong> green beans</strong> and <strong>Tenderstem broccoli </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until the vegetables are starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1659433187685-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1659433187685-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1659433187685-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1659433187685-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1659433187685-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have started to soften, stir through the <strong>drained noodles</strong> and the <strong>black bean sauce </strong>and cook for 1 min further or until the sauce has warmed through – these are your <strong>black bean noodles</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1659433192346-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1659433192346-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1659433192346-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1659433192346-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1659433192346-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> crispy five-spice salmon </strong>with the <strong>black bean noodles </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
